52
00:03:23,540 --> 00:03:24,880
That's ridiculous...

53
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:28,040
Okay! I'm gonna build a raft and paddle all the way there!

54
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,540
That's what you just thought up!

55
00:03:30,740 --> 00:03:32,240
It's done!

56
